{"tid":1849041,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"曾經有一份至真嘅愛情擺喺我面前，但我冇去珍惜","createTime":"2020-01-28T21:05:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T09:30:58.000Z","uid":35484,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f9b1f4db8b86706b5321178a9533419df730c906","tid":1849041,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T21:05:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=1&amp;v=jCHrIINcTQE&amp;feature=emb_logo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D1%26v%3DjCHrIINcTQE%26feature%3Demb_logo&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JssFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=450723a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=1&amp;v=jCHrIINcTQE&amp;feature=emb_logo</a><br />\n曾經有一份至真嘅愛情擺喺我面前，但我冇去珍惜，到冇咗嘅時候先至後悔莫及--塵世間最痛苦莫過於此。如果個天可以畀個機會我番轉頭嘅話--我會同個女仔講我愛佢，如果係都要喺呢份愛加上一個期限--我希望係一萬年<br />\n<br />\n原來被一個人全心全意咁去愛，係一件全世界最最最幸福既事<br />\n感謝你當時不留後路的真情，感謝你永遠坦誠的品質，感謝你離別時的輕盈瀟灑，與你相戀，是我這輩子最大幸事，也是最大的遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n希望下世可以比我照顧你，愛你，錫你一生一世比幸福你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39dac7a0d5084afd8820828b763ae1be0c52aa35","tid":1849041,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T21:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95eba09bd84ec19b19ac0128d92ce5553acfd5c2","tid":1849041,"uid":268774,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T21:29:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24654135f20a10b218e2be0ee4871f38ba925009","tid":1849041,"uid":136015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T21:31:10.000Z","msg":"我希望我可以用一世俾幸福佢"},{"pid":"40833f08db182a476742e311c87bfbf78996db91","tid":1849041,"uid":18791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f9b1f4db8b86706b5321178a9533419df730c906","tid":1849041,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"